    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You stepped into a building that seemed oddly familiar yet deeply unsettling. As you turn back to leave, reality shifts - you are trapped, looping endlessly through eerie corridors and spaces that defy logic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your only hope is an elevator that promises an exit. Each level holds subtle yet disturbing anomalies things that shouldn’t exist, things out of place. Observe carefully, choose floors wisely, or risk the chance of getting trapped forever. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liminal Exit is an atmospheric walking simulator deeply inspired by liminal spaces, offering a uniquely unsettling experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you find the real exit, or remain trapped in liminality forever?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&gt; <strong>PLAY TIME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35 - 90 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/2e0d7fba8bc2749b0dcfbab469932780.poster.avif?t=1763489917\" width=780 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/2e0d7fba8bc2749b0dcfbab469932780.webm?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/2e0d7fba8bc2749b0dcfbab469932780.mp4?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; ESCAPE THE LOOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way out from the endlessly repeating environments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/9cc5e8915939f0e527537589398de5bd.poster.avif?t=1763489917\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/9cc5e8915939f0e527537589398de5bd.webm?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/9cc5e8915939f0e527537589398de5bd.mp4?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>&gt; LOOK FOR ANOMALIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keen observation is key to identifying subtle disturbances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/56648c3471dc9216a2a3c61eeaf3bd55.poster.avif?t=1763489917\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/56648c3471dc9216a2a3c61eeaf3bd55.webm?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/56648c3471dc9216a2a3c61eeaf3bd55.mp4?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; AVOID BLISS AT ALL COST</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't be too comfortable in the environment. That might be a trap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/742dd7b309dddc87792c6980dbc0cad6.poster.avif?t=1763489917\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/742dd7b309dddc87792c6980dbc0cad6.webm?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044220/extras/742dd7b309dddc87792c6980dbc0cad6.mp4?t=1763489917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
